hotelDescription:
In a valley surrounded by wooded hills, this relaxed hotel is 5 km from Dakshinkali Temple, 18 km from Kathmandu Durbar Square and 21 km from Tribhuvan International Airport.
 Set in thatched-roof cottages, the 6 simple rooms offer sitting areas, en suite wet rooms, and verandas with hillside views.
 There's an unfussy vegetarian restaurant with a terrace and views of the valley. Breakfast, parking and Wi-Fi are available. A generator is on-site.
